	(3, 'Terms & Conditions', '<p><strong>Terms of using the services of&nbsp;</strong><a href="https://bridge2capital.com/"><strong>www.bridge2capital.com</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;and /or mobile application Bridge2capital</strong></p>', '<p><strong>1.Introduction</strong><br />\r\n <br />\r\n 1.1 Your use of this website / mobile application (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;Application&quot;) and all service and products (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Services&quot;) is subject to these terms, which may be amended from time to time at the sole discretion of the Xtracap Fintech India Pvt. Ltd (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;Company&quot;) without an prior intimation to you.<br />\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n <strong>2.Accepting the Terms</strong><br />\r\n <br />\r\n 2.1 You shall interact with parties concerned through this Application. By clicking a button or check box, where this option is made available to you on the Application, you accept and agree to the terms set out herein to avail the Services.<br />\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n <strong>3.Provision of the Services through Application</strong><br />\r\n <br />\r\n 3.1 The Application is an online and digitally enabled financial technology service that helps you process your working capital demand and online payments with the financial institutions registered with Reserve Bank of India. The Company is not a bank or a Non-Banking Financial institution, and does not represent or warrant that it seeks to or is capable of providing services for banking and allied activities by its self. Your usage of the Application is at the sole discretion of the Company.<br />\r\n <br />\r\n 3.2 The provision of Services is entirely subject to you paying a non-refundable annual subscription fee to the Company at such rate as may be communicated to you by the Company for services provided through the mobile technology application by the Company. The company also has the option of charging an additio